#about-foundation
  h2.header-light More about the foundation

  .row
    .col-sm-6
      p The Mozilla Foundation was established in July 2003 as a California not-for-profit corporation dedicated to the public benefit. The Mozilla Foundation also wholly owns the subsidiary organization, the Mozilla Corporation.

      p The Mozilla Foundation is guided by the principles of the Mozilla Manifesto.

      h3.header-light Organization

      p The Mozilla Foundation is a California non-profit corporation exempt from Federal income taxation under IRC 501(c)(3). It is governed by its Board of Directors.
